{"lemma":"عَرَبُ","slug":"عَرَبُ","root":"ع.ر.ب","root_slug":"ع-ر-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ر-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"عَرَبُ","root":"عرب","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":6,"pos_tags":["adj","noun","verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":10},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n28530","n28535","n28537","n28539"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to translate into Arabic"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to Arabicize, Arabize; to give an Arabic form"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to express, to state clearly, to declare; to put in plain Arabic"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to upbraid, to disapprove of, to declare foul","tags":["obsolete"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to lop, to prune, to scarify and cauterize or otherwise trim at the surface","tags":["obsolete"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"Arabs, true Arabs","tags":["collective"]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"masculine plural of عَرَبِيّ (ʕarabiyy)","tags":["form-of","masculine","plural"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to give earnest money"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to express sexual desire towards, to attempt to render desirous of copulation, to be obscene towards","tags":["obsolete"]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"plural of عَرُوب (ʕarūb)","tags":["form-of","plural"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Denominal verb of عَرْبُون (ʕarbūn).\n\nDenominal verb of عَرُوب (ʕarūb)."},"ipa":["/ʕar.ra.ba/","/ʕa.rab/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n28530","headword_ar":"عرّب","root":"Erb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEoriybN","text_ar":"تَعْرِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(an Arab)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"arabicized"},{"kind":"text","text":"a foreign word;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spoke it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pronounced it, agreeably with the ways of Arabic speech;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AErb","text_ar":"اعرب","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, *) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iEoraAbN","text_ar":"اـِعْرَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He taught"},{"kind":"text","text":"another"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the Arabic language."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA, from a trad.) ―         -b3-  See also 4, in fourteen places. ―         -b4-  The inf. n. signifies also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"showing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"declaring, one's saying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one's deed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to be bad, evil, abominable,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foul."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Er~b Ealayohi","text_ar":"عرّب عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He showed him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"declared to him, that his saying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his deed, was bad,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.; and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upbraided him for it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEalotu ka*aA waka*aA famaA Ear~aba EalaY~a A^aHadN","text_ar":"فَعَلْتُ كَذَا وَكَذَا فَمَا عَرَّبَ عَلَىَّ اَحَدٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I did so and so, and no one upbraided me;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"charged me with having acted disgracefully."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Er~b Ealayohi fiEolahu","text_ar":"عرّب عَلَيْهِ فِعْلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qawolahu","text_ar":"قَوْلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He showed him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"declared to him, that his deed was bad, evil, abominable,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foul,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O,) and so"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"his saying."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEoriybN","text_ar":"تَعْرِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"saying to a man who has uttered what is foul,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"erroneous,"},{"kind":"text","text":"“"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It is not so, but so;"},{"kind":"text","text":"”"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"telling him what is more correct."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sh, TA.) And The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"replaying against a speaker;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iEoraAbN","text_ar":"اـِعْرَابٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Er~b Ealayohi","text_ar":"عرّب عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He replied against him, denying"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disallowing"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disapproving what he said:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he prevented, hindered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"forbade, him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he did so, and denied"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disallowed"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disapproved"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what he said"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"did"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) [See what next follows.] ―         -b5-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"treating medically, to remove his disease, one whose stomach is in a corrupt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"disordered, state."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K. [In both,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~aEoriybu","text_ar":"التَّعْرِيبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is expl. as meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tamoriyDu AlEaribi","text_ar":"تَمْرِيضُ العَرِبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al*~aribi AlmaEidapi","text_ar":"الذَّرِبِ المَعِدَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". Freytag has strangely rendered the verb as signifying “"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ægrotum reddidit"},{"kind":"text","text":"aliquem stomachi corruptio. ”]) Az says that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~aEoriybu","text_ar":"التَّعْرِيبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"followed by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY","text_ar":"عَلَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"and having for its object him who says what is disapproved may be from this. (TA.) ―         -b6-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lopping a palm-tree;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pruning it by cutting off some of its branches."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K. *) ―         -b7-  And The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scarifying"},{"kind":"text","text":"a horse or similar beast"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the parts of the skin next the hoofs and then cauterizing those parts:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cauterizing"},{"kind":"text","text":"a horse"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in several places in those parts, and then gently scarifying them without producing any effect upon the sinews,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tendons,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, O, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in order to strengthen the"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1992},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"parts,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Az, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in order that the hair may become strong:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Er~b Alfarasa","text_ar":"عرّب الفَرَسَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he made an incision in the bottom of the horse's hoof;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and the verb implies that, by this operation, what was concealed becomes apparent to the eye, so that one knows the state of the hoof, whether it be hard or soft, sound or diseased. (L, TA. See also 1 in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"bzg","text_ar":"بزغ"},{"kind":"text","text":".)       -A2-  Also, the inf. n., The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"getting,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"procuring for oneself, an Arabian horse."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA. [See also 4, near the end.]) ―         -b2-  And The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"taking,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"making, for oneself, an Arabian bow."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K.)       -A3-  Also the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drinking much clear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"limpid, water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K,) which is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Earib","text_ar":"عَرِب"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O.)       -A4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Er~b Albaqarapa","text_ar":"عرّب البَقَرَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEorabahaA","text_ar":"اَعْرَبَهَا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He rendered the cow desirous"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of copulation"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; said of a bull. (O, K.)       -A5-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Er~b","text_ar":"عرّب"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Fr, Mgh, O,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taEoriybN","text_ar":"تَعْرِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Fr, O, K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AErb","text_ar":"اعرب","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Fr, Mgh, O, Msb,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iEoraAbN","text_ar":"اـِعْرَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Fr, Mgh, K;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Earobana","text_ar":"عَرْبَنَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (O, and S and K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Erbn","text_ar":"عربن"},{"kind":"text","text":";)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He gave what is termed an"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eurobuwn","text_ar":"عُرْبُون"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, Msb, K) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EurobaAn","text_ar":"عُرْبَان"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Fr, Mgh) [i. e. an"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"earnest"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY ka*aA","text_ar":"فِى كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the case of such a thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (O,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY bayoEihi","text_ar":"فِى بَيْعِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the case of his purchase"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Msb.) One says, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEorabuwA","text_ar":"اَعْرَبُوا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY Ald~aAri A^arobaEamiAy^apK","text_ar":"فِى الدَّارِ اَرْبَعَمِايَةٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They paid in advance, as an earnest, in the case of the house, four hundred"},{"kind":"text","text":"[dirhems]. (L, TA.) It is related in a trad. that ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA_iEoraAb","text_ar":"الاـِعْرَاب","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"in buying and selling is forbidden: (Mgh, O, TA:) this is said by Sh to mean A man's"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"saying to another, If I do not purchase this for so much, thou shalt have such and such of my property."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","K","TA","Az","Fr","Mgh","Msb"]},{"entry_id":"n28535","headword_ar":"عَرْبٌ","root":"Erb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iEoraAbN","text_ar":"اـِعْرَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ifoSaAHN","text_ar":"اـِفْصَاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[but app. as a subst. (not an inf. n.) meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Clear, plain,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"distinct, speech"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiraAbapN","text_ar":"عِرَابَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v. (TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EarabN","text_ar":"عَرَبٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"as"},{"kind":"text","text":"[inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eariba","text_ar":"عَرِبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"na$aATN","text_ar":"نَشَاطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Briskness, liveliness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sprightliness"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (O, K.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n28537","headword_ar":"عِرْبٌ","root":"Erb","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such as is dried up, of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"species of barley-grass called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buhomaY","text_ar":"بُهْمَى"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, O, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of any herb,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"leguminous plant:"},{"kind":"text","text":"n. un. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":": or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eirobu AlbuhomaY","text_ar":"عِرْبُ البُهْمَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the prickles of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"buhomaY","text_ar":"بُهْمَى"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","O","K"]},{"entry_id":"n28539","headword_ar":"عَرِبٌ","root":"Erb","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"[part. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eariba","text_ar":"عَرِبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.: as such signifying]"},{"kind":"page_break","n":1994},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Having the stomach in a bad,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"corrupt, state."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maEidapN EaribapN","text_ar":"مَعِدَةٌ عَرِبَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A stomach in a bad,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"corrupt, state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from being burdened."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  Also, and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EarabN","text_ar":"عَرَبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, K,) the former of which is the more common, (TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EurobubN","text_ar":"عُرْبُبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Abundant"},{"kind":"text","text":"water, (O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"such as is clear,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"limpid."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nahorN EaribN","text_ar":"نَهْرٌ عَرِبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAribN","text_ar":"عَارِبٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAribapN","text_ar":"عَارِبَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A river containing abundance of water."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biy^orN EaribapN","text_ar":"بِيْرٌ عَرِبَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A well containing much water."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaribapN","text_ar":"عَرِبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to a woman: see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaruwbN","text_ar":"عَرُوبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in four places. ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEarabu","text_ar":"العَرَبُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEaribapu","text_ar":"العَرِبَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEaribaAtu","text_ar":"العَرِبَاتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEarabu","text_ar":"العَرَبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", first quarter."}],"source_refs":["S","O","TA","K"]}]}}